title: Postcards from Buster, Season 1 (DVDRip)
description:
Arthur's best friend Buster is starring in his own series! Buster will accompany his airline pilot father as he flies the fictional Latin rock group Los Viajeros on a concert tour of the United States, with forays into Canada, Mexico, and Puerto Rico. Buster will stay in touch with his friends back at home with a small, hand-held digital video camera.

Ripped directly from the S01 DVDs. MP4 format with complete iTunes tagging.
(They come with an iTunes-compatible M4V extension. If your player only recognizes the MP4 extension, change it.)
